    slug: "no-underscore-names",
    title: "No Underscore Names",
    summary: "Variable and class names must not contain underscores.",
    markdown:
      "# no-underscore-names\n\nVariable and class names must not contain underscores.\n\n## Bad\n\n```typescript\nconst user_name = 'Alice';\nclass My_Service {}\n```\n\n## Good\n\n```typescript\nconst userName = 'Alice';\nclass MyService {}\n```\n\n## Why\n\nUnderscores conflict with the camelCase and PascalCase conventions used throughout TypeScript codebases. Consistent naming reduces cognitive overhead.",
    ruleSourcePath: "packages/guardrails/src/rules/no-underscore-names/rule.ts",
